{"tid":1569231,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【8.31屍殺列車】眾新聞追訪6名沒被捕乘客　重組速龍太子站無差別襲擊市民","createTime":"2019-09-14T14:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T03:39:13.000Z","uid":212626,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5b03f639d16a7ab60fd329222eb1404bde3e536f","tid":1569231,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:09:06.000Z","msg":"8月31日晚上，速龍及防暴警察進入港鐵太子站月台及車廂追捕示威者，「屍殺列車」場面震驚公眾。警方事後解釋，稱是接獲報案才入站執法，前線警員根據現場市民報料及其「專業判斷」，例如見到「遮陣」、有人襲擊警察行為，便以武力制止。警方多次否認毆打無辜市民。<br />\n<br />\n然而，眾新聞找到6名當晚在場的市民，他們願意受訪，包括5名親歷「屍殺列車」的乘客。從他們的證詞可見，是速龍先在月台用槍及胡椒噴霧瞄向車廂內的乘客，後者才嚇至開遮自衛；乘客未有作出任何攻擊行為，速龍及防暴警察就突然衝入車廂打人，之後並沒有當場拘捕車廂內的乘客。他們質疑警方純粹為發洩情緒，而「無差別」襲擊市民。<br />\n<strong>Andy拍攝得速龍舉槍指向車廂乘客，當時車廂尚未出現「遮陣」：</strong><br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GXSzPS7cE00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGXSzPS7cE00&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=337cb51d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GXSzPS7cE00</a><br />\n警察陸續離開車廂時，Peter將Jane及女友人推往另一車廂，Jane一邊哭，一邊用手機拍下車廂的情況：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gn1ltxmNidY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGn1ltxmNidY&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=3cd1abb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gn1ltxmNidY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23506/831警察太子站打人-速龍小隊-逃犯條例-23513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F23506%2F831%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E6%89%93%E4%BA%BA-%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-23513&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=7b2704ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23506/831警察太子站打人-速龍小隊-逃犯條例-23513</a>"},{"pid":"ead94b26ea56d7cdc1d225b27f3f287cd90dc47e","tid":1569231,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:09:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d913909059a4ed7ee79bf4fdb9ed2cb2f37cf5af","tid":1569231,"uid":221265,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5b03f639d16a7ab60fd329222eb1404bde3e536f","tid":1569231,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:09:06.000Z","msg":"8月31日晚上，速龍及防暴警察進入港鐵太子站月台及車廂追捕示威者，「屍殺列車」場面震驚公眾。警方事後解釋，稱是接獲報案才入站執法，前線警員根據現場市民報料及其「專業判斷」，例如見到「遮陣」、有人襲擊警察行為，便以武力制止。警方多次否認毆打無辜市民。<br />\n<br />\n然而，眾新聞找到6名當晚在場的市民，他們願意受訪，包括5名親歷「屍殺列車」的乘客。從他們的證詞可見，是速龍先在月台用槍及胡椒噴霧瞄向車廂內的乘客，後者才嚇至開遮自衛；乘客未有作出任何攻擊行為，速龍及防暴警察就突然衝入車廂打人，之後並沒有當場拘捕車廂內的乘客。他們質疑警方純粹為發洩情緒，而「無差別」襲擊市民。<br />\n<strong>Andy拍攝得速龍舉槍指向車廂乘客，當時車廂尚未出現「遮陣」：</strong><br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GXSzPS7cE00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGXSzPS7cE00&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=337cb51d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GXSzPS7cE00</a><br />\n警察陸續離開車廂時，Peter將Jane及女友人推往另一車廂，Jane一邊哭，一邊用手機拍下車廂的情況：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gn1ltxmNidY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGn1ltxmNidY&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=3cd1abb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gn1ltxmNidY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23506/831警察太子站打人-速龍小隊-逃犯條例-23513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F23506%2F831%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E6%89%93%E4%BA%BA-%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-23513&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=7b2704ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23506/831警察太子站打人-速龍小隊-逃犯條例-23513</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:10:26.000Z","msg":"其實真係要喺國際做文宣<br />\n香港人知嘅都知道"},{"pid":"3bada4c4b667038d2ad5f271887529590d2f65d5","tid":1569231,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"<strong>速龍挑釁乘客：「出嚟吖！出嚟吖！」</strong><br />\n到底此前發生了什麼事？是什麼觸動速龍的神經？<br />\n<br />\nDaniel記得，當時乘客與速龍曾有一輪口角，雙方情緒激動，但他們幾個朋友並沒有加入口角。Jackson憶述：「<span style=\"color: red;\">（乘客）叫（速龍）唔好開槍</span>、走呀。好多說話喺耳邊出嚟，但唔係好確定佢哋講啲乜嘢。講得最多係：<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好射呀，呢度全部都係市民嚟㗎</span>。都聽到有啲話：<span style=\"color: red;\">我咩都冇做過</span>。」<br />\n<br />\nDaniel認為，現場警察頗為失控，乘客手持雨具已刺激到他們，<span style=\"color: red;\">有速龍在月台挑釁車廂內的乘客</span>，但乘客未有理會。從米報攝影師梁柏堅拍攝影片01:25－01:30可見，警員向車廂內的乘客近距離舉槍及胡椒噴霧後，兩名速龍向車廂內的乘客招手，其中一名速龍說：「出嚟吖！出嚟吖！」<br />\n<br />\n車門多次開合，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中一次車門打開，速龍突然用警棍猛打雨傘，旋即向人群噴胡椒噴霧</span>。站在最前排的Andy首當其衝，雙眼中椒，Jackson及Ivan即時將他拉到後排。原本在車門的人群散向車廂兩邊，Andy、Jackson和Ivan躲到架起「遮陣」的一邊，Daniel與另外數名乘客「落單」在另一邊。兩邊的人都捱了一陣亂棍和胡椒噴霧。<br />\n<br />\n數名速龍隨後經另一扇車道進入車廂，Daniel頓時被多名速龍包圍，身體多處被警棍打中。「嗰幾秒之間，我唯一諗嘅就係點樣走，我一路跳返入後面安全啲嘅地方（遮陣內）。佢打嘅時候，我原本揸住把遮，佢打一下，把遮已經彎晒，我揸住把遮都冇用。」Daniel重申，他一直沒有攻擊警員，即使被打亦未曾還手。<br />\n<br />\n在同一車廂，Jane與男朋友Peter以及另一名女友人在距離車門較遠的位置。速龍及防暴警察會衝入車廂時，Peter用身體護著 Jane及女友人，掩著二人的頭部，Jane視線受阻擋，未能看清楚整個環境，「但（警察）好明顯打緊人，其中一個男仔畀人扑緊頭，流晒血。」<br />\n<br />\nJane 感覺<span style=\"color: red;\">當時警察在車廂上打人時，並沒有特定的目標</span>，「<span style=\"color: red;\">佢（警察）打緊嗰個狀態，根本冇理你係咩人</span>。冇打到我哋3個，係因為真係好彩冇打到，而唔係佢揀過，覺得我哋3個冇嘢，所以唔打。」"},{"pid":"d7044233ccd42298cc1f66eac7ce86cfa1993c04","tid":1569231,"uid":281342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y31tg5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy31tg5b.jpg&h=af101f74&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LPoZ8bS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLPoZ8bS.jpg&h=25b70c67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29fde4e88992a48e5c0ee59c1a898c95284500a1","tid":1569231,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:12:39.000Z","msg":"據Daniel、Jackson、Ivan所見，車廂內一片狼藉，一名男子被打至前額直流血，速龍及防暴警察並沒有從車廂內帶任何人到月台；當時Andy雙眼視野模糊，完全看不到車廂的情況。<br />\n<br />\nJackson 由始至終都不理解何以發生「屍殺列車」，「你（警察）拘捕或行使武力之前，都要講點解要對我哋行使武力，但佢咩都冇講到，就用胡椒噴霧射你、用棍打你。入嚟車廂打你幾棍就出去，我覺得成件事完全係唔合理。如果你有合理懷疑，譬如我似係示威者，戴晒頭盔、上晒豬咀，好full gear咁樣，你打我、捉我出去，我覺得比較合理少少囉。」Daniel指，速龍及防暴警察當時根本沒有意欲拘捕車廂內的乘客，打人純粹為發洩情緒。「如果佢有拘捕意圖，其實我哋嗰陣已經完全冇還手、反抗之力，佢可以成車都拉晒。」<br />\n<br />\n他們所在的荃灣線列車，在車門幾次開、合之後，在晚上11時04分駛離太子站，開往油麻地站。而在3號月台的觀塘線列車，亦在3分鐘後、11時07分駛往石硤尾站。一眾受訪者最終各自從油麻地站及石硤尾站離開港鐵回家，未有被捕。<br />\n<br />\n大律師公會9月3日發聲明，批評警方在無合理的情況下，以暴力對待太子站內的市民，包括向月台及車廂的乘客以「無差別」的方式施放胡椒噴劑及以警棍毆打，而其後警員離開車廂時，並沒有作出任何拘捕。"},{"pid":"f5df9b8aa960b4b7d5d7d9f4100b358254d1ea32","tid":1569231,"uid":288372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:14:25.000Z","msg":"藍絲暴力得到警方保護，大家分d人改一下擾亂敵手。每一次有製造到絕對的恐懼才可以壓制，否則藍絲有恃無恐。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kox4z06.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkox4z06.png&h=f4484784&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7cf25675fe42d1cff7e39f427697c030336fa5b","tid":1569231,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140d8d3542f64442b25365743172cd28f05f8a2d","tid":1569231,"uid":108902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84edc00266aba254aa904d6b18b63894ff9a934","tid":1569231,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:17:22.000Z","msg":"篇新聞好長 所以我只係copy咗一部份過嚟<br />\n嗰兩條應該係新公開嘅片<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec7feb9cdd182fc04c86f5fbcf2462e0aa4c91a","tid":1569231,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7502cb062178f2c754f6b7b933ba23310656f230","tid":1569231,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:17:31.000Z","msg":"831<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2d128b27bc74cb6d34099278f5916683d25d71","tid":1569231,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a8f3d2e41bca58caabcafce90aad53cfeefe70","tid":1569231,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:19:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"164873d7a61b2087044067e50fb8fc75524f484c","tid":1569231,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:20:17.000Z","msg":"有藍絲搞事就係想大家唔理831<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a291ce46bcbf0592dca3e0c8b3a02c46a06739f0","tid":1569231,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:20:37.000Z","msg":"打咪打 使擇日<br />\n<br />\n係真喎"},{"pid":"5ade62ba2f6619d404b22989430e641fa569de23","tid":1569231,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:23:13.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地開心啦，尋晚中秋前線小朋友食得一個包咋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567456</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5390974bbee5139bb508cb087899d28ed3340893","tid":1569231,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:23:28.000Z","msg":"同一時間，53歲的廚師吳志輝（細輝）正在月台。他在下班回家途中。他從荔枝角站上車，乘坐荃灣線列車到太子站，準備轉乘觀塘線。細輝在太子站月台聽到「緊急廣播」後，未及離開，<span style=\"color: red;\">一批速龍從後而至，一手將他推倒</span>。他聽到該批奔跑中的速龍說：<span style=\"color: red;\">「嗰度有個full gear」</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">「嗰度有人著黑衫」</span>。他知道速龍並非要制伏、拘捕他，只是視他為「障礙」，故將他推開，再繼續追捕前方一個黑衣人。細輝指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">速龍以年輕人為目標，特別是穿黑衣、戴口罩、身上有裝備者</span>，他們一到月台就大舉追捕，將目標壓落地，<span style=\"color: red;\">以警棍打、用腳踢</span>。他認為月台不安全，及後躲到觀塘線列車一卡車廂中。"},{"pid":"31ff2c24ca9ff2ef8d51e6b21ca48f4366617454","tid":1569231,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96bdee582f8e7e8211397dcf394cc9c847d05250","tid":1569231,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:26:56.000Z","msg":"我哋喺車廂度企咗好耐，諗住等車門閂，一開始係以為有人阻住車門。好多人同我哋一樣，都係塞喺車廂度，<span style=\"color: red;\">當時架列車係全滿咁濟</span>。」他們在列車中後段的一卡車廂內，完全不知道車頭位置有乘客衝突。Daniel憶述，他們在車廂內呆等一段時間後，聽到港鐵廣播：「噹、 噹、 噹。緊急廣播：由於發生嚴重事故，本站將會關閉，乘客必需立即離開。所有閘機現已開啟，出閘毋須使用車票或八達通卡。」他們出到月台，見到連屏幕都轉成螢光粉紅色，<span style=\"color: red;\">「嗰時個氣氛好恐怖。」</span>當時Andy、Daniel、Ivan都是穿著白衣、 Jackson 穿著黃衣，都沒有戴口罩，更沒有頭盔、眼罩等防禦裝備。"},{"pid":"c71afbd52090d8fe3b315f43260224f2cb1cda55","tid":1569231,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ae67777e63232719f3235d786ea7549c7725bc","tid":1569231,"uid":111898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:57:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dd605d9148917adf8cf23e70367d863a9494cd78","tid":1569231,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:10:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n第五期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1</a><br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=a829c82a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"f91f7c22bde118b8da998ca1a4fb270a7cc877d3","tid":1569231,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355ad85e0b7a083d19a83b400ce5dc674bbbde23","tid":1569231,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"老細，你一日開十幾條新聞po，想必831當日都一直睇住直播<br />\n有無覺得當日的情況好鬼？從立法會一直打到灣仔，就算有過百汽油彈同幾米高的大火，班黑警都表現得極其剋制，所有野都跟足規範，次次開槍都舉旗<br />\n<br />\n當時我睇直播睇到心都灰曬，覺得呢次林鄭大條道理立緊急法，而且唔會引起非議；點知班黑警去到11點鐘左右，突然衝入太子對市民進行無差別毆打，同之前的專業剋制大相徑庭。呢單野都搶曬汽油彈和大火，成爲國際輿論頭條。<br />\n<br />\n個人完全解釋唔到，兄台有何高見？"}]}